  .container.margin-top-25
    .row
      .col-md-3
        h2.section-title RESEARCH
      .col-md-9
        p
        p We tried to be effective during our research phase, making it short and useful. We gathered data from user feedback, reports, and competitive analysis. We continued to create assumptions that we later validated with surveys and interviews of the staff.
        p The client and staff had needs, but customers too. Trying to get those goals aligned to scoping which features would be useful to them, what goals do they need to accomplish as a Staff and what are the customer needs and desires.
        .margin-top-25
        
