  hr
  .container.margin-top-25
    .row
      .col-md-3
        h2.section-title Persona Development
      .col-md-9
        p
        p Our users are admins, they work in the doing customer support for the cleaning service company. They should take calls from client complains, take the information down and make decisions like provide refunds, assign new cleaners, create assignments and give them rewards. Their role is to assist the customer with all their needs, have a clear and fast understanding of the complete the company.
        p To test our ideas and hypothesis, we created some profiles of the often employees. Testing helped understand possible scenarios and to see which functions could be useful.
        p We also created profiles of the customers and their needs and goals, even though they are not using the application. Having a perspective of their goals is what is going to drive us to make a useful product.
        
        .margin-top-25
        
